---
<section id="destaques" class="py-16 container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-samavi-dark mb-3">Destaques da Semana</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Confira algumas das novidades que acabaram de chegar na nossa loja física.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gray-200 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555041469-a586c61ea9bc?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop');"></div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-samavi-red uppercase tracking-wider">Sala de Estar</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-1 mb-2 text-gray-900">Sofá Retrátil Confort</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Estrutura reforçada, tecido suede de alta qualidade e máximo conforto para a sua família.</p>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic">Disponível na Loja</span>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/5533988774411?text=Olá,%20gostaria%20de%20saber%20mais%20sobre%20o%20Sofá%20Retrátil%20Confort" target="_blank" class="bg-samavi-red text-white text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-900 transition-colors">
                        Consultar Preço
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gray-200 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615874959474-d609969a25ed?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop');"></div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-samavi-red uppercase tracking-wider">Sala de Jantar</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-1 mb-2 text-gray-900">Mesa Elegance 6 Lugares</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Design moderno com tampo em vidro e cadeiras estofadas ergonômicas para suas refeições.</p>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic">Disponível na Loja</span>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/5533988774411?text=Olá,%20gostaria%20de%20saber%20mais%20sobre%20a%20Mesa%20Elegance" target="_blank" class="bg-samavi-red text-white text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-900 transition-colors">
                        Consultar Preço
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gray-200 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540518614846-7ede433c4ef0?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop');"></div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-samavi-red uppercase tracking-wider">Quarto</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-1 mb-2 text-gray-900">Conjunto Box Premium</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">Noites de sono revigorantes com tecnologia de suporte avançada para a sua coluna.</p>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic">Disponível na Loja</span>
                    <a href="https://wa.me/5533988774411?text=Olá,%20gostaria%20de%20saber%20mais%20sobre%20o%20Conjunto%20Box" target="_blank" class="bg-samavi-red text-white text-sm font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-900 transition-colors">
                        Consultar Preço
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>